query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(dd i inv cs) */ select i.i_item_id,
i.i_item_desc,
i.i_current_price
from inventory AS inv
inner join item AS i
on inv.inv_item_sk = i.i_item_sk AND inv.inv_quantity_on_hand BETWEEN 100 AND 500 AND i.i_current_price BETWEEN 22 AND 22 + 30 AND i.i_manufact_id IN (678,
964,
918,
849)
inner join date_dim AS dd
on dd.d_date_sk = inv.inv_date_sk AND dd.d_date BETWEEN '2001-06-02'::date AND '2001-08-01'::date
inner join catalog_sales AS cs
on cs.cs_item_sk = i.i_item_sk group by i.i_item_id, i.i_item_desc, i.i_current_price order by i.i_item_id LIMIT 100;
